       <p class="style11" awml:style="Style11" dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;text-indent:0.3937in"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'" xml:lang="-none-" lang="-none-">Инвестиции &nbsp;в повышение эффективности</span></p>
      </td>
